XmppBot: Web
------------

This is a web interface for XmppBot (http://github.com/trilader/xmppbot)
The interface itself has no special dependencies other than PHP 5 or
greate with the SQLite3 module enabled.

Installation
------------

Just copy the files in the repository where your webserver can find it.
Make a copy of "config.inc.php.example" and name it "config.inc.php" and
you are done. 

Configuration
-------------

The configuration of the web interface is simple and all options are
stored in the file "config.php.inc" which can be found in the same
directory as this file.

All options in the configuration file are described there.
